author: Unreal Engine
description:
Watch this video and find out how Unreal Engine was used to create the painterly look of the motion graphics for WWE’s Clash in Paris.

The Graphics and VFX team at WWE TV Production had just two weeks to render out 400 deliverables for the Clash in Paris wrestling extravaganza. 

This video dives into how UE5 helped them hit the deadline—and how they were able to achieve a stunning Van Gogh-style look in the engine. 

You can read all about it here: 
https://epic.gm/spotlight-wwe-clash-in-paris

#MotionGraphics, #WWE, #ClashInParis, #VanGogh, #UnrealEngine, #UE5
title: UE5 lays the smackdown on long rendering times for WWE’s Clash in Paris
